OL,3,CBoy who died after being hit by
OL,4,Cvehicle 'brought light to our lives',
OL,5,Cfamily say
OL,7,FA 12-year-old boy who died after being
OL,8,Fhit by a vehicle in Essex "brought
OL,9,Flight and life into all our lives",
OL,10,Fhis grieving family said in a tribute.
OL,12,FEssex Police said that Bobby
OL,13,FBloomfield sustained serious injuries
OL,14,Fafter he was hit by a vehicle in
OL,15,FPilgrims Hatch on Sunday and died a
OL,16,Fshort time later in hospital.
OL,18,FA 15-year-old boy and a 43-year-old
OL,19,Fman, both from the Pilgrims Hatch
OL,20,Farea, were arrested on suspicion of
OL,21,Fmurder, the force said on Monday.
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@bO]
