OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781115078
OL,3,CBoy who died after being hit by
OL,4,Cvehicle 'brought light to our lives',
OL,5,Cfamily say
OL,7,FPolice said on Tuesday that their
OL,8,Fdetention period has been extended
OL,9,Fafter the force secured a magistrates'
OL,10,Fwarrant.
OL,12,FOfficers had been called to the
OL,13,FAshwells Road area shortly before
OL,14,F5.40pm on Sunday.
OL,16,FIn a statement released through police
OL,17,Fon Tuesday, Bobby's family said:
OL,18,F"Losing a child is every parent's
OL,19,Fnightmare.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
