OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781115078
OL,3,CBoy who died after being hit by
OL,4,Cvehicle 'brought light to our lives',
OL,5,Cfamily say
OL,7,F"We are living that nightmare and no
OL,8,Fwords can ever explain how we are
OL,9,Ffeeling.
OL,11,F"Bobby brought light and life into all
OL,12,Four lives and we have lost that
OL,13,Fforever.
OL,15,F"The hole he has left can never be
OL,16,Ffilled.
OL,18,F"We would ask for our privacy to be
OL,19,Frespected as we pull together as a
OL,20,Ffamily at this horrific time."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOUzD@AOU|D@^O]
