OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781115078
OL,3,CBoy who died after being hit by
OL,4,Cvehicle 'brought light to our lives',
OL,5,Cfamily say
OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Greg Wood,
OL,8,Fwho is overseeing the investigation,
OL,9,Fsaid: "Our investigation team has been
OL,10,Fworking around the clock as they
OL,11,Fcontinue to build a complete picture
OL,12,Fof the tragic incident on Sunday.
OL,14,F"This is not straightforward work and
OL,15,Fthere are complexities involved which
OL,16,Fof course we cannot explore publicly
OL,17,Fat this stage.
OL,26,@qD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
