CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781115078
OL,3,CBoy who died after being hit by
OL,4,Cvehicle 'brought light to our lives',
OL,5,Cfamily say
OL,7,F"This work has included the review of
OL,8,Fa significant amount of CCTV and
OL,9,Fobtaining key evidence from those
OL,10,Fnearby.
OL,12,F"This work is key to ensuring we
OL,13,Funderstand all aspects of the incident
OL,14,Fas we progress."
OL,16,FChief Inspector Terry Fisher,
OL,17,FBrentwood district commander, said:
OL,18,F"We are acutely aware this incident is
OL,19,Fattracting commentary on social media.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUvD@PO]zD@AOU
