OL,3,CBoy who died after being hit by
OL,4,Cvehicle 'brought light to our lives',
OL,5,Cfamily say
OL,7,F"I would again like to urge the public
OL,8,Fto please respect a grieving family's
OL,9,Fprivacy at this terrible time.
OL,11,F"We are doing all we can to ensure
OL,12,Fthey are supported both now and in the
OL,13,Fcoming weeks and months."
